<br>
Then he spots Ellywig across the way. She looks vaguely familiar to him -- perhaps he met her in passing? Ah, he sees she has a water elemental -- his favorite kind.<br>
<br>
Gnosis saunters over to Ellywig and offers to buy her a drink. After the initial awkward introductions, he explains the Unified Theory of elemental summoning, whereby elements can be summoned from different planes, then combined in this plane. He suggests that perhaps the bubbles are the result of summoning an air elemental within a water elemental.<br>
<br>
He notices that Ellywig is eyeing him suspiciously. She must realize he has no clue what he is talking about. Quickly, Gnosis turns to the barkeep and orders her another spiked egg nog, in the hopes of distracting her from his bullplop theory.<br>
