<br>
Banging her hand down on the bar, she calls, &quot;Gnomish spirits, please!&quot;  While waiting for her drink, she looks around for any sign of life in the tavern.  Not even a bard was present to lift their spirits with a song.  But, who knows, perhaps Kimaya will come by with some of that wonderful brew she brought last week.  Maritizia's spirits rise just thinking about it.  Who knows what mischief they can cause tonight.<br>
<br>
Several heads turn in her direction as Maritzia quietly giggles into her drink...<br>
