<br>
&quot;Leave it to a ranger to have the smart-arse remark, and yea, shut the damn door, will ya? <p><center><img src="http://pic3.picturetrail.com/VOL18/605666/942834/10971516.jpg"><BR>art by Luis Royo</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uburanmcmuffin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>BuranMcMuffin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 50<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/1/02 7:43:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=79.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Out of Place</span><hr size=1> *I chuckle quietly, finish my sip of cocoa, then speak up*<br>
