<br>
 <p>Maritzia Soulhealer<br>
29th Season Cleric of Rodcet Nife<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=traxxus>Traxxus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 256<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/12/02 6:02:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=79.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Out of Place</span><hr size=1> Traxxus had seen Maritzia barge into the bar and had been watching with some amusement as she poured herself further and further into the bottle. He had taken in a few ales himself, but only enough to calm his nerves and relax his tired muscles. He'd been in the field for weeks, he had grown adept at living off the land and seldom returned to town. His was the life of a lonely adventurer, usually traveling with only his wits, bow, and blades for protection.<br>
<br>
He had been enjoying this period of respit. He'd secured a room, cleaned himself up, and was taking some time to share the company of the local townsfolk.<br>
<br>
He watched as Maritzia stood, he knew her dismount wouldn't end well.  As she stumbled he quickly covered the ground between them and deftly slipped his hands beneath her to keep her head from hitting the floor. Although he'd spent most of his life hunting alone, he'd learned that it's never a good thing to let a cleric get badly injured.<br>
<br>
Traxxus hefted Maritzia's limp form onto his shoulder. He then turned to the barkeep, placed a few platinum on the bar and asked for a second room.  This young lady would need a safe place to sleep off her stupor.<br>
<br>
After depositing her lithe form upstairs and securing her room, Traxxus returned to his table and once again lost himself in the ramblings of several adventurers sharing the tavern.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=79.topic&start=21&stop=21>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=79.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=79.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=79.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.threadControl?topicID=79.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=79.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=79.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm9">OT/OOC Forum<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm58">Telegrams!<option value="firionaviefrm47">Guild